K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-0: @348b dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-1: sems can khams ni mtha' yas pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-2: sdug bsngal nye bar zhi ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-3: ngan 'gro rnams las bsgrol ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-4: nyon mongs rnams las sgrol ba'i phyir; ;srid pa mi bde dog pa na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-5: sdug bsngal sna tshogs ci mchis pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-6: de ltas yongs su bskyab pa'i phyir //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-7: bdag gis byang chub sems bskyed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-8: sems can phongs pa thams cad kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-9: skyabs su bdag nyid rtag tu shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-10: bdag ni mgon med rnams kyi mgon //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-11: rten med rnams kyi rten du bdag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-12: skyabs med rnams kyi skyabs 'gyur zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-13: sdug bsngal bde bar byed pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-14: bdag ni sems can thams cad kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-15: nyon mongs zhi bar byed par shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-16: dge ba'i las rnams gang dang gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-17: 'di dang gzhan du bsags pa rnams //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-18: bsod nams ye shes zhes bya ba'i; ;tshogs ni rnam pa gnyis su shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-19: pha rol phyin pa drug sgo nas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-20: bdag gis brtson 'grus gang brtsams pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-21: de yang sems can ma lus pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:348b-22: thams cad la ni phan par shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-0: @349a *// tshe yi mtha' klas byed pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-1: gang yang cung zad byed 'gyur ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-2: mdor na sems can thams cad kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-3: nyon mongs thams cad zhi ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-4: grol bar bya ba'i phyir 'bad cing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-5: byang chub rab tu dga' brtson no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-6: de nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-7: cho ga bzhin du kun tu bskyed //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-8: sems can kun dang snying rje dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-9: byams pa nye bar gnas par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-10: sems ni legs par sbyang ba'i phyir //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-11: sna tshogs thabs kyis rjes dran drug //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-12: nang gi bdag nyid zhi ba yis //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-13: bsam pa gcig tu bsgom par bya //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-14: sngon gyi rgyal ba'i sras rnams kyi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-15: smon lam ji ltar mdzad pa bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-16: bdag kyang dge ba'i sems kyis su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-17: de bzhin du ni smon lam 'debs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-18: chos kyi longs spyod sna tshogs la //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-19: mnyam par bzhag nas yid rang ngos //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-20: sems can thams cad bde ba dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-21: zhi zhing nad kyang med par shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-22: bdag ni bya ba kun nus shing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-23: yon tan dang yang ldan par shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-24: nor ldan gtong phod shes rab can //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-25: bzod ldan dge la dad pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-26: sems can tshe rabs thams cad du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-27: skye ba dran zhing brtser ldan shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-058:349a-28: dpal legs par grub par byed pa'i rgyud chen po las 'byung ba'i smon lam rdzogs so ////
